      <hedline>
        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Men with guns come and wreak havoc on a very regular basis. Those men cause more death by making people flee their homes than actually by shooting or slitting throats.''</p>
        <p>LES ROBERTS, supervisor of a survey that attributes 1.7 million deaths in eastern Congo to two years of war. [A1]</p>
      </block>
